
Building for iMX6 with a generic toolchain:

  $ NOCONFIGURE=1 ./autogen.sh
  $ ./configure --host=arm-linux-gnueabihf --prefix=/opt/test
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

Building at host:

  $ NOCONFIGURE=1 ./autogen.sh
  $ ./configure --prefix=/usr CFLAGS="-DFORCE_TEST_SYSFS -DFORCE_TEST_LEVELS"
  $ make
  $ sudo make install
